{"tid":1418268,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位認清局勢，軍政府已經暗中成立","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:18:56.000Z","uid":270871,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e254f9f29d1e41ffa74d6660f90dcd791075baa2","tid":1418268,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"以下內容屬於推測<br />\n不過軍政府你以為係講笑？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">埃及、也門、蘇丹等等都係革命革到變軍政府掌權，前車可鑑</span><br />\n<br />\n8月5號林鄭宣佈警察會每日開記者會<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係每日呀！</span></span><br />\n呢啲係咩招數嚟？<br />\n係查維斯、毛澤東呢類獨裁者嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">搞祟拜搞造神嘅手段</span><br />\n霸佔新聞版面迫你日日對住佢<br />\n無論有無事都要你對住佢、聽佢發噏瘋<br />\n同宣佈警察正式掌權冇咩分別<br />\n<br />\n如果你想話警察唔係一個人，係一堆政見不一嘅人<br />\n咁示威者又何嘗唔係？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋政治立場接近統一，親中、仇恨示威者<br />\n而且有共同利益，就係最怕俾人清算<br />\n咁又點會冇可能掌權呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n宜家有可能控制局勢嘅只有警察同中共<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">中共唔願意負上出解放軍直接接管香港政府嘅後果</span><br />\n當然亦都唔想回應示威者嘅五大訴求<br />\n所以會縱容警察為所欲為<br />\n對中共嚟講呢個係最安全嘅選項<br />\n<br />\n如果林鄭宣佈成立一個真嘅獨立調查委員會<br />\n我相信佢會即刻俾警察踢落台<br />\n所以林鄭只係個傀儡，警察政府嘅傀儡<br />\n<br />\n對示威者嚟講<br />\n訴求除咗要過中共嗰關之外，更加要過警察嗰關<br />\n而警察當然會反對雙普選<br />\n因為選舉結果好明顯，大家都會用獨立調查委員會嚟拉票（民調話79%人支持）<br />\n而且佢哋掌緊權點解要同你分權<br />\n<br />\n警察已經唔止係政權嘅最後防線<br />\n仲成為咗政權本身<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以無論你係要革命推翻政府定只係要求回應訴求<br />\n你都係必須要過警察嗰關</span>"},{"pid":"f044c06442cc473da249c1f916ffbd2844f15dbc","tid":1418268,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:20:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190803/59819998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59819998&d=bDHmYwogulq9FkNLxWxOtjBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=29f245e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190803%2F59819998&h=c440f64c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190803/59819998</a><br />\n黑警嘅金主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c8651dfb87f7bb60b5cb70fe6947a84c7acc44","tid":1418268,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:24:44.000Z","msg":"軍政府唔係流<br />\n<br />\n如無意外林鄭同佢班子已被架空"},{"pid":"4ec33490678e9e5db05010916e91af71076e89d2","tid":1418268,"uid":267039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:27:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90dee027257f7eb0d7080944962edd68a55a5f8a","tid":1418268,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ffe76df204a2c533e9d9d9e612d1d5378bf83d9","tid":1418268,"uid":138446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:37:08.000Z","msg":"&lt;全部人同我入黎&gt; 下一步 廢除公安條例<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418362</a>"},{"pid":"490f11512a242d145a6ffc36b3abddf1a6f1301a","tid":1418268,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1093d55d2372df45f5795ad67b8c24b8b725b754","tid":1418268,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:18:56.000Z","msg":"push"}]}